@startuml
[*] --> Registered : register or log in with details
Registered --> TeacherMode : continue as a teacher
Registered --> StudentMode : continue as a student
TeacherMode --> CreateQuiz : create a new quiz
TeacherMode --> EditQuiz : edit an existing quiz
TeacherMode --> SaveDraftOrPost : save as draft or post for students
SaveDraftOrPost --> ViewResults : view quiz results after posting
StudentMode --> SelectQuiz : select a quiz to answer
SelectQuiz --> AnswerQuiz : answer the selected quiz
AnswerQuiz --> SubmitQuiz : submit the answered quiz
SubmitQuiz --> ViewResult : view result after submitting quiz

@enduml
